org.owasp.jsptester.conf.tagproperties.ui
Class TagInfoListCellRenderer

java.lang.Object
  org.owasp.jsptester.conf.tagproperties.ui.TagInfoListCellRenderer
All Implemented Interfaces:
ListCellRenderer
public class TagInfoListCellRenderer
extends Object
implements ListCellRenderer

List cell renderer that allows JList to render a TagInfo element. Functions as a wrapper (adapter) by using the given ListCellRenderer (ListCellRenderer if non provided) and populating the cell with the String name of the tag.

Author:
Jason Li
